{"tid":715820,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［求指教］黎緊6月尾第一次去布吉7日","createTime":"2018-06-24T19:04:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T03:47:00.000Z","uid":177924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b72492cfe10de637eff21f45a093f26e5d9682f3","tid":715820,"uid":177924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T19:04:16.000Z","msg":"黎緊6月尾同朋友7個人去布吉玩一個禮拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n住拉威既Airbnb<br />\n由於我地都係第一次去布吉/泰國<br />\n所以想係到問下巴打絲打一啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. local tour方面大家係去到先報定係上網報定？因為睇返我地去果7日既天氣都唔係幾穩定，如果去到睇返天氣再報會唔會比較好？如果天氣問題取消既話有無得退錢？同埋網上報既話有無人用過travelfever?好唔好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 行程方面大家有無咩好推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第一次去唔係好識安排，\b有無咩係建議去食去玩<br />\n<br />\n3. \b因為我地無人有車牌，想問下大家係用咩call車app<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好多問題，如果有去過布吉既巴打絲打可以分享下就感激不盡啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b5d7485e6d0aea70fd01e9c54ca0daee02c402","tid":715820,"uid":96068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T19:23:03.000Z","msg":"Crab call車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d895dec31430c3615ced86b3e3815d6a5fe87278","tid":715820,"uid":96068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"05b5d7485e6d0aea70fd01e9c54ca0daee02c402","tid":715820,"uid":96068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T